flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 25: Smart Reorder Point Calculation and Alert Routing

  Trigger[GET /api/ai/reorder/:productId]
  Inputs[Collect Inputs\nAvg Daily Demand from forecast\nLearned Lead Time\nDemand StdDev\nDays to Festival\nWeather Regime]

  Formula1[ROP equals Avg Daily Demand x Lead Time plus Safety Stock]
  Formula2[Safety Stock equals Z 1.65 x StdDev x sqrt of Lead Time]
  Formula3[Apply Multipliers\nfestival if days_to_festival < 14\nweather if monsoon-sensitive category]

  Compute[Compute reorder_point\nreorder_quantity\nurgency_flag]
  StockCheck{stock_on_hand <= reorder_point?}

  AlertYes[Create Context-Aware Alert\nWhatsApp + In-App]
  PersistAlert[(Persist Alert and Notification Intent)]
  ActionYes[Recommend Immediate Restock\nVendor Dashboard CTA]

  NoAlert[Return ROP payload only\nNo urgent action]

  LeadTimeCheck{Lead-time history available?}
  LeadTimeFallback[Use default lead-time policy\nMark lower confidence]

  Trigger --> Inputs --> LeadTimeCheck
  LeadTimeCheck -- Yes --> Formula1
  LeadTimeCheck -- No --> LeadTimeFallback --> Formula1

  Formula1 --> Formula2 --> Formula3 --> Compute --> StockCheck

  StockCheck -- Yes --> AlertYes --> PersistAlert --> ActionYes
  StockCheck -- No --> NoAlert
